Architecture
------------
Language: Go 1.22+
CLI      : Cobra (cmd/)
Modules  : internal/{database,fetcher,processor,scraper,config}
Database : SQLite; sqlc generates type-safe code in internal/database

Testing
-------
Run all tests          : go test ./...
Verbose                : go test -v ./...
Package-specific       : go test ./<pkg>/...
Coverage report        : go test -cover ./...
Mocks (when changed)   : mockery --all --output internal/mocks

Linting / Quality
-----------------
Format code            : go fmt ./...
Static analysis        : go vet ./...
Optional (if enabled)  : golangci-lint run

